name: Cleaning Up
overview: Three cleaning ladies at an investment firm get their hands on insider stock information and hatch a chance on a scheme that could change their lives.

episodes.name: Episode 1
episodes.overview: Yong-mi, who is suffering from a predicament, overhears Tae-kyung's secret phone call, who is misusing inside information. Faced with a once-in-a-lifetime opportunity, Yong-mi takes a step into the back alley of the financial markets for a 'normal life'.

episodes.name: Episode 2
episodes.overview: Yong-mi discovers a side of Suja he shouldn't have seen! However, for some reason, Soo-ja behaves differently from Yong-mi's expectations, and Yong-mi and In-kyung use the information they obtained after the twists and turns to invest in stocks for the first time in their lives. Meanwhile, Taekyung detects a strange sound coming from inside the ventilator...!

episodes.name: Episode 3
episodes.overview: As things get worse, In-kyung and Yong-mi leave Bestid to find new jobs. Worse, Yongmi is in danger of losing his children. Yong-mi decides to find out the name of the 3D printer company to bring his kids...

episodes.name: Episode 4
episodes.overview: Yong-mi is undecided between the two companies, so what's Yong-mi's choice? In-kyung accidentally gets Tae-kyung's project call, and Yong-mi hides her identity and attends an insider meeting. However, an unexpected person appears...!

episodes.name: Episode 5
episodes.overview: Yongmi's heart almost exploded when he met grass in an unexpected place. Yongmi escapes the crisis on his own terms at the insider meeting. Yong-mi, In-kyung, and Su-ja begin a plot to infiltrate the Ilwon Foundation to obtain information...

episodes.name: Episode 6
episodes.overview: Jan Di finds out that Yongmi's real identity is Bestid beauty salon! Pushed by a bend, Yong-mi makes an unexpected offer to Jung-dang. Meanwhile, Yong-mi, In-kyung, and Su-ja, who have successfully completed their first joint operation, are having fun, but shadows of the past begin to fall on Yong-mi...

episodes.name: Episode 7
episodes.overview: Between Sooja and Inkyung, who are happy at the rice cake table, Yong-mi can't help but smile alone. Young-shin proposes to Yong-mi a secret project that only Tae-kyung and the two of them work on. Yong-mi tries to find a breakthrough through Young-shin's suggestion.

episodes.name: Episode 8
episodes.overview: Jan Di approaches In-Kyung to find Tae-Kyung's lost project phone. Yong-mi is invited to Young-shin's house and has fun, but when the short-selling project enters an unexpected phase, she makes the choice she wants to avoid the most.

episodes.name: Episode 9
episodes.overview: Young-sin finds the gap Yong-mi was hiding and tries to open Yong-mi. Soo-ja and In-kyung find out about Yong-mi's condition. In-kyung gets drunk and knocks on Yong-mi's door. Meanwhile, Yong-mi begins to prepare to send the kids away.

episodes.name: Episode 10
episodes.overview: Yong-mi is caught by Song Woo-chang! Will Yong-mi be able to escape Song Woo-chang's grasp? Yong-mi is saddened by Young-sin's disappointment even in a time of crisis, and In-kyung is surprised by Doo-young's unexpected appearance at the end of despair.

episodes.name: Episode 11
episodes.overview: Yong-mi is afraid of Song Woo-chang's threats, and to make matters worse, In-kyung and Soo-ja get angry when Yong-mi is advised to resign. Young-shin and Yong-mi, knowing that Song Woo-chang will not stop, start to float their chances ...

episodes.name: Episode 12
episodes.overview:
The independence of the three of them is ambitious, but it's not as easy as they think!

Yong-mi wants to bring the kids, but things don't go well, and Geum Jan-di proposes to Yong-mi for a collaboration once again. Yong-mi, In-kyung, and Soo-ja start a new project, but face an unexpected ambush...

episodes.name: Episode 13
episodes.overview: With Young-shin's sudden appearance, the situation moves forward without knowing what to expect. Yong-mi and Young-shin set a date for each other, and Young-shin accepts the inevitable offer. On the other hand, Yongmi and Inkyung held a special event for estranged Souza on their birthday.

episodes.name: Episode 14
episodes.overview: Yong-mi once again tries to confirm the death of Song Woo-chang from Jan-di. Doo-young wants to give In-kyung a special gift, but she's flustered by the unexpected reaction. Dong-joo notices a suspicious connection between Yong-mi and Jan-di! Thanks to this, Yong-mi comes face to face with an unexpected character.

episodes.name: Episode 15
episodes.overview: When Woo-chang's threat extends to Yun-a, Yong-mi proposes a deal with Woo-chang. As operations continue, share prices rise, but Suja and Inkyung are unhappy for their own reasons. Meanwhile, an unexpected casualty occurred due to the manipulation of Wuchang's stock price...
